{
  "stem": "16163.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he became a very strong man later on, one of those things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, my parents spoke a little French.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had friends from France who lived, at that particular time, in Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the only thing I really heard was German, no Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We celebrated the holidays.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not from a religious background.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had a synagogue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And had-- I don't know if it was a cantor or a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We called him rabbi.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for the holidays, we would go to shul.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we had Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Heller, Max Heller.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he left just before the war and came here to the states.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then later, we had somebody, Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lazarus, I believe was his name, yeah, Lazarus.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, just was a synagogue in Vlotho, Vlotho synagogue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If it had a name, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yes, as a matter of fact, it was quite a big synagogue for a small little place like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was so few Jews living there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in that area, were a lot of resorts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in those resort areas, just happened not to be many Jewish people living there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they came for the holidays to Vlotho.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My favorite Jewish holiday?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Passover.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because-- because there was wine on the table.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as children, we didn't get any wine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my mother made some kind of a fruit juice at the time, and told me that that was mine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, usually, Gunter and his brother came over too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had Passover together, and with his parents, naturally.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were thinking that we were drinking wine, and always thought we were [YIDDISH], which we were not.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Being drunk, that much Jewish I know-- knew then already.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
